  {
    "id": "000a6507-bf20-4051-b91b-60a69f824c2a",
    "type": "text",
    "content": {
      "text": "Supported by wakeboarding athletes Pedro Zucki and Gustavo Reichert, the action merged human skill with the unmatched capability of the L200 Triton and Eclipse Cross. The Reconquest also launched Mitsubishi's new 4You4Challenge platform, dedicated to empowering athletes to push the limits of what is possible."
    },
